   <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">This procedure applies to all Space personnel, contractors and visitors, and all operations including manufacturing facilities, technical centers, offices and administrative buildings where work activities expose personnel to falls from heights.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Working At Heights is applicable any time an Space employee is working at unprotected elevations as specified by local regulation. The Working At Heights process does not apply to work performed on ladders or approved scaffolding.</li>
